description:
Rapper, ChellaH joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote her latest singles "Frozen," & "You Can See It" featuring Shawnna. The ladies discuss a range of topics including ChellaH's son being aware of her raunchy lyrics, ChellaH faking the holy ghost, revenge cheating, and much more.
